textAfterTable: Profile Daishin Enriching Equity Investment Trust is an open-end fund incorporated in Korea. The objective of the Fund is to achieve capital incomes and current incomes. The Fund invests 60% or more in stocks, 40% or less in bonds, 40% or less in ABSs, and 40% or less in CPs.
